{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a pre-checkout eligibility form with a one-question-at-a-time view (step-by-step format). The form should include these questions in order:
    
    1. Full name, DOB(date select not text input), ID/passport (grouped together in one step)
    2. Current health status (radio buttons)
     -Great
     -Generally Okay
     - Not goodera
    3. Medical conditions (multi-select with "None" as exclusive option)
     -Heart Disease
     -Diabetes
     -Hypertension
     -Other (add text box to specify other)
    4. Medications/allergies (short text input)
    5. Main goal (radio buttons: weight, anti-aging, gut, energy, injury, immune, other)
    6. Pregnancy/breastfeeding (Yes/No radio buttons)
    7. "Have you ever had a serious reaction to any peptide, hormone or weight-loss injection?" (Yes/No radio buttons)
    8. Consent checkbox (required): "I confirm my information is true and I consent to doctor review."
    
    The form should display one question per screen with Next/Previous navigation buttons, show progress indicator, validate required fields before allowing progression, and have a clean, professional medical form design. I want to be able to add options per questions and edit them.
    
    Preferred answers
    
    Health status - Great or Good
    Medical condition - None
    Pregnant / Breastfeeding - No
    Serious reaction - No
    
    Green-light (auto-approve) rules - Show Checkout button
    Auto-route to “Approved by doctor” if ALL are true:
    Age within your safe range (e.g., 21–65, customisable).
    “Current health” = Great or Generally okay.
    No serious conditions ticked (e.g., no heart disease, no active cancer, no severe GI disease if starting GLP-1s, etc.).
    Medications/allergies field = “None” or only low-risk meds.
    Not pregnant/breastfeeding.
    No previous adverse reaction to peptides (you can add a yes/no question if you want).
    
    Red-flag rules (force manual review) Show message and no chckout button
    Route to “Doctor must review before script” if ANY are true:
    Serious chronic condition box ticked (heart disease, severe kidney/liver disease, autoimmune, complex GI, etc.).
    Pregnancy/breastfeeding = Yes.
    “Other serious condition” chosen.
    Medications/allergies field includes certain keywords you define (e.g., anticoagulants, insulin, chemo, etc.).
    Age outside your preferred range.
    On the backend, show this clearly:
    Status: Auto-clear – Awaiting doctor signature
    Status: Red flag – Doctor review required
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-eligibility-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
    padding: 40px;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.text_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.text_font.fallback_families }};
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__progress-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__progress-bar-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 8px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.progress_bg_color }};
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__progress-fill-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.progress_fill_color }};
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__progress-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__step-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
    animation: ai-eligibility-form-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__step-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    display: block;
  }

  @keyframes ai-eligibility-form-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__question-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.question_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__input-group-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.input_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus {
    outline: 2px solid {{ block.settings.primary_color }};
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__radio-group-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-group-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.input_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover,
  .ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    border-color: {{ block.settings.primary_color }};
    background-color: {{ block.settings.option_hover_bg }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}.selected,
  .ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}.selected {
    border-color: {{ block.settings.primary_color }};
    background-color: {{ block.settings.option_selected_bg }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }} input[type="radio"],
  .ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }} input[type="checkbox"] {
    margin-right: 12px;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }} label,
  .ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }} label {
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-grow: 1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__other-input-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__other-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__consent-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.consent_bg_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.input_border_radius }}px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__consent-{{ ai_gen_id }} input[type="checkbox"] {
    margin-top: 4px;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__consent-{{ ai_gen_id }} label {
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__navigation-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__button-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_text }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__button-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.secondary_button_hover }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__button-next-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.primary_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_text }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__button-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_hover }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.error_color }};
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }}.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__result-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__result-{{ ai_gen_id }}.visible {
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__result-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__result-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}.approved {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.success_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.success_color }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__result-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}.review {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.warning_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.warning_color }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__result-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__result-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__result-message-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__checkout-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 16px 40px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.primary_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_text }};
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__checkout-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.primary_button_hover }};
  }

  .ai-eligibility-form__date-inputs-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-eligibility-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .ai-eligibility-form__question-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.question_size | times: 0.85 }}px;
    }

    .ai-eligibility-form__date-inputs-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<eligibility-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-eligibility-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-eligibility-form__progress-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-eligibility-form__progress-bar-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__progress-fill-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-progress-fill></div>
    </div>
    <div class="ai-eligibility-form__progress-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-progress-text>Step 1 of 8</div>
  </div>

  <form data-eligibility-form>
    <div class="ai-eligibility-form__step-{{ ai_gen_id }} active" data-step="1">
      <h2 class="ai-eligibility-form__question-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step1_question }}</h2>
      
      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__input-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <label class="ai-eligibility-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}" for="full-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Full name *</label>
        <input 
          type="text" 
          id="full-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
          name="full_name" 
          class="ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          required
          data-field="full_name"
        >
      </div>

      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__input-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <label class="ai-eligibility-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Date of birth *</label>
        <div class="ai-eligibility-form__date-inputs-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <select 
            name="dob_day" 
            class="ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            required
            data-field="dob_day"
          >
            <option value="">Day</option>
            {% for i in (1..31) %}
              <option value="{{ i }}">{{ i }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
          </select>
          <select 
            name="dob_month" 
            class="ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            required
            data-field="dob_month"
          >
            <option value="">Month</option>
            <option value="1">January</option>
            <option value="2">February</option>
            <option value="3">March</option>
            <option value="4">April</option>
            <option value="5">May</option>
            <option value="6">June</option>
            <option value="7">July</option>
            <option value="8">August</option>
            <option value="9">September</option>
            <option value="10">October</option>
            <option value="11">November</option>
            <option value="12">December</option>
          </select>
          <select 
            name="dob_year" 
            class="ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            required
            data-field="dob_year"
          >
            <option value="">Year</option>
            {% assign current_year = 'now' | date: '%Y' | plus: 0 %}
            {% for i in (0..100) %}
              {% assign year = current_year | minus: i %}
              <option value="{{ year }}">{{ year }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__input-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <label class="ai-eligibility-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}" for="id-passport-{{ ai_gen_id }}">ID/Passport number *</label>
        <input 
          type="text" 
          id="id-passport-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
          name="id_passport" 
          class="ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          required
          data-field="id_passport"
        >
      </div>

      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-error>Please fill in all required fields</div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-eligibility-form__step-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-step="2">
      <h2 class="ai-eligibility-form__question-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step2_question }}</h2>
      
      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.health_option_1 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-radio-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              id="health-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="health_status" 
              value="{{ block.settings.health_option_1 }}"
              data-field="health_status"
            >
            <label for="health-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.health_option_1 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.health_option_2 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-radio-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              id="health-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="health_status" 
              value="{{ block.settings.health_option_2 }}"
              data-field="health_status"
            >
            <label for="health-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.health_option_2 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.health_option_3 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-radio-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              id="health-3-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="health_status" 
              value="{{ block.settings.health_option_3 }}"
              data-field="health_status"
            >
            <label for="health-3-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.health_option_3 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-error>Please select an option</div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-eligibility-form__step-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-step="3">
      <h2 class="ai-eligibility-form__question-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step3_question }}</h2>
      
      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.condition_option_1 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-checkbox-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="checkbox" 
              id="condition-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="medical_conditions" 
              value="{{ block.settings.condition_option_1 }}"
              data-field="medical_conditions"
            >
            <label for="condition-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.condition_option_1 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.condition_option_2 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-checkbox-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="checkbox" 
              id="condition-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="medical_conditions" 
              value="{{ block.settings.condition_option_2 }}"
              data-field="medical_conditions"
            >
            <label for="condition-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.condition_option_2 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.condition_option_3 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-checkbox-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="checkbox" 
              id="condition-3-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="medical_conditions" 
              value="{{ block.settings.condition_option_3 }}"
              data-field="medical_conditions"
            >
            <label for="condition-3-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.condition_option_3 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.condition_option_4 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-checkbox-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="checkbox" 
              id="condition-4-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="medical_conditions" 
              value="{{ block.settings.condition_option_4 }}"
              data-field="medical_conditions"
            >
            <label for="condition-4-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.condition_option_4 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-checkbox-wrapper>
          <input 
            type="checkbox" 
            id="condition-other-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
            name="medical_conditions" 
            value="Other"
            data-field="medical_conditions"
            data-other-trigger
          >
          <label for="condition-other-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Other</label>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-eligibility-form__other-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-other-input>
          <input 
            type="text" 
            name="medical_conditions_other" 
            class="ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            placeholder="Please specify"
            data-field="medical_conditions_other"
          >
        </div>
        {% if block.settings.condition_none != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__checkbox-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-checkbox-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="checkbox" 
              id="condition-none-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="medical_conditions" 
              value="{{ block.settings.condition_none }}"
              data-field="medical_conditions"
              data-none-option
            >
            <label for="condition-none-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.condition_none }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-error>Please select at least one option</div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-eligibility-form__step-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-step="4">
      <h2 class="ai-eligibility-form__question-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step4_question }}</h2>
      
      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__input-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <textarea 
          name="medications_allergies" 
          class="ai-eligibility-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          rows="4"
          placeholder="List any medications or allergies, or type 'None'"
          required
          data-field="medications_allergies"
        ></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-error>Please fill in this field</div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-eligibility-form__step-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-step="5">
      <h2 class="ai-eligibility-form__question-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.step5_question }}</h2>
      
      <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.goal_option_1 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-radio-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              id="goal-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="main_goal" 
              value="{{ block.settings.goal_option_1 }}"
              data-field="main_goal"
            >
            <label for="goal-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.goal_option_1 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.goal_option_2 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-radio-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              id="goal-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="main_goal" 
              value="{{ block.settings.goal_option_2 }}"
              data-field="main_goal"
            >
            <label for="goal-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.goal_option_2 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.goal_option_3 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-radio-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              id="goal-3-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="main_goal" 
              value="{{ block.settings.goal_option_3 }}"
              data-field="main_goal"
            >
            <label for="goal-3-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.goal_option_3 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.goal_option_4 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-radio-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              id="goal-4-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="main_goal" 
              value="{{ block.settings.goal_option_4 }}"
              data-field="main_goal"
            >
            <label for="goal-4-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.goal_option_4 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.goal_option_5 != blank %}
          <div class="ai-eligibility-form__radio-option-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-radio-wrapper>
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              id="goal-5-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
              name="main_goal" 
              value="{{ block.settings.goal_option_5 }}"
              data-field="main_goal"
            >
            <label for="goal-5-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.goal_option_5 }}</label>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.goal_option_6 != blank %}
